README: 90 participants between the ages of 8 and 25 performed value-directed memory encoding and retrieval tasks. Full details of the tasks can be found in Nussenbaum, K. & Hartley, C.A. (2021). Developmental change in prefrontal cortex recruitment supports the emergence of value-guided memory. eLife.
